				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
			<h4 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Selling a company in the foodservice industry?</h4>		</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-5f4d556 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="5f4d556" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
								<div class="elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix">
				<p>Whether a restaurant chain, a supplier, or a technology company, an M&amp;A Advisor will significantly contribute to getting a fair valuation — and reduce risk — rewarding what has been built and the pipeline of potential.</p>					</div>
