				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
			<h4 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">We support with both sell-side mandates and middle-market buy-side advisory for restaurant and foodservice industry investments. </h4>		</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-d74ec69 elementor-widget elementor-widget-button" data-id="d74ec69" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="button.default">
